<F P=100> Sub-Saharan Africa </F>
<H3> <TI>   Angolan Foreign Minister Arrives on Official Visit </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2903100494 Beijing XINHUA in English 0909 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2903100494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 29 (XINHUA) -- Foreign Minister of 
the Republic of Angola Venacio da Silva Moura and his party 
arrived here this morning for a five-day visit to China at the 
invitation of Chinese Vice-Premier and Foreign Minister Qian 
Qichen. 
  This is the first China visit made by an Angola foreign 
minister since the two countries established diplomatic ties in 
1983. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

