<F P=100> Near East &amp; South Asia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Qian Qichen, Libyan Foreign Liaison Secretary Discuss Ties </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3003090994 Tripoli JANA in English 0817 GMT 30 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD3003090994 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli JANA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

