Language: <F P=105> Burmese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A 10-member Bangladeshi delegation led by 
Chittagong Divisional Commissioner Mr. Omar Farouq arrived at 
Sittwe [Akyab] airport by helicopter at 0945 yesterday to attend 
the 16th high-level Myanmar [Burma]-Bangladesh Border Meeting. 
