<DOCNO> FBIS3-4684 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas040__a94013" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-040-A </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  1 March 1994 </DATE1>

