Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, February 28 (KCNA) -- Malian President 
Alpha Oumar Konare and Equatorial Guinean Prime Minister 
Silvestre Siale Vileka, when they met with the DPRK ambassadors 
some time ago, expressed support to the just cause of the Korean 
