  Rigoberto Padilla Ruz, general secretary of the Central 
Committee of the Communist Party of Honduras, when he received 
the DPRK ambassador to Nicaragua on February 22, said that the 
proposal for reunification through confederacy advanced by the 
great leader Comrade Kim Il-song is the most realistic and just 
overture. He said he would always extend support and solidarity 
to the Korean people in their struggle for the reunification of 
the country. 

